Decision Tree

Overall Summary

Decision Tree performed better then logistic regression with overall accuracy of 0.8 both on Train and Test data. Logistic on the other hand performed with accuracy of 0.7 for both test and train data . So clearly, Decision TRee perfroms better then Logistic
